<!--

  Subscriptions are handled by an external service for simplicity. I chose
  ConvertKit as it seemed both cheap and easy to set up. Other options include:

  * follow.it - honestly deemed it as too good to be true
  * SendPulse - very appealing pay-as-you-go model instead of a subscription
  * EmailOctopus - the free plan is great, but requires their own branding
  * listmonk - open source with support for AWS SES, but also harder to set up
  * sendy.co - similar as above, but pay-once model
  * MailerLite - good free plan, but no 2FA and still has branding

-->

